OL,4,CAntoine Griezmann: Atletico Madrid
OL,5,Caccuse Barcelona of 'disrespect'
OL,6, Atletico Madrid have accused Antoine
OL,7, Griezmann and Barcelona of "disrespect"
OL,8, and say the La Liga champions talked to
OL,9, their forward in March.
OL,11,FAtletico say they have rejected
OL,12,FBarcelona's offer and ordered Frenchman
OL,13,FGriezmann to report for pre-season.
OL,15,FIn a statement, the Madrid club
OL,16,Fexpressed their "strongest repulsion
OL,17,Ffor the behaviour of both, especially
OL,18,FBarcelona".
OL,20,FGriezmann, 28, said in May he would
OL,21,Fleave Atletico this summer.
